{"tid":948813,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"新發現兩棲動物取名「特朗普」　諷忽視全球暖化","createTime":"2018-12-20T10:48:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-23T11:26:30.000Z","uid":28765,"like":7,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"687e6824e5f26859ed6a207b12ea6c2311d5a3ac","tid":948813,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20181220/s00005/df1fdabbdf3266795511fb162cadbb97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20181220%2Fs00005%2Fdf1fdabbdf3266795511fb162cadbb97.jpg&h=7a1b8c37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n美洲國家巴拿馬新發現一種穴居兩棲動物，有環保建築材料公司的創辦人以2.5萬美元（約19.6萬港元）投得其命名權，並取名為「Dermophis donaldtrumpi」，以暗諷美國總統特朗普（Donald Trump）在全球暖化的取態有如「失明」。<br />\n<br />\n新發現的兩棲動物屬一種蚓螈，沒有雙目和會把頭埋在沙堆中，其命名權拍賣為組織「Rainforest Trust」籌款，有科學家已使用該名字，正式在科學文獻上公布發現成果。「Rainforest Trust」表示，這種兩棲動物容易受全球暖化影響，「與其同名的人所推出的氣候政策，會導致牠有滅絶的危險」。<br />\n<br />\n奪得命名權的環保建築材料公司「EnviroBuild」聯合創辦人貝爾（Aidan Bell）表示，蚓螈一詞取自拉丁語「caecus」，意即「失明」，反映特朗普對氣候變化的取態。他又說，「Dermophis donaldtrumpi」將頭埋在沙堆中的能力，與特朗普對全球暖化的取態脗合。公司又將特朗普一頭標誌性的金髮，以改圖形式拼到該動物的照片中。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普曾指全球暖化是騙局，上任後又宣布美國退出《巴黎協定》，備受爭議。<br />\n<br />\n（衛報／英國廣播公司）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181220/s00005/1545274258368/%E6%96%B0%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%85%A9%E6%A3%B2%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%96%E5%90%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E3%80%8D-%E8%AB%B7%E5%BF%BD%E8%A6%96%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9A%96%E5%8C%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181220%2Fs00005%2F1545274258368%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25A3%25B2%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%2590%258D%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%25AB%25B7%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%259A%2596%25E5%258C%2596&d=Z2jMhz2b9l4CHI9OUTtYFZ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=be1dc4a9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%2Farticle%2F20181220%2Fs00005%2F1545274258368%2F%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%2599%25BC%25E7%258F%25BE%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25A3%25B2%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%2589%25A9%25E5%258F%2596%25E5%2590%258D%25E3%2580%258C%25E7%2589%25B9%25E6%259C%2597%25E6%2599%25AE%25E3%2580%258D-%25E8%25AB%25B7%25E5%25BF%25BD%25E8%25A6%2596%25E5%2585%25A8%25E7%2590%2583%25E6%259A%2596%25E5%258C%2596&h=806e1f90\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B/article/20181220/s00005/1545274258368/%E6%96%B0%E7%99%BC%E7%8F%BE%E5%85%A9%E6%A3%B2%E5%8B%95%E7%89%A9%E5%8F%96%E5%90%8D%E3%80%8C%E7%89%B9%E6%9C%97%E6%99%AE%E3%80%8D-%E8%AB%B7%E5%BF%BD%E8%A6%96%E5%85%A8%E7%90%83%E6%9A%96%E5%8C%96</a>"},{"pid":"700b038a7cdd3dcff229e3dbf101913e8fb944b8","tid":948813,"uid":94828,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"幾時有新種狗<br />\n改佢叫習近平"},{"pid":"eb024d70add8e6981765e0557aebbf7e2e10dbd2","tid":948813,"uid":82450,"like":13,"dislike":1,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:51:28.000Z","msg":"P得好差<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/clown2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95dc62d29c1f77e06b74ef77f6240e66d0a0f0e0","tid":948813,"uid":146340,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:51:52.000Z","msg":"依隻嘢絕埋種地球都未暖化啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c77174b9911cf3c1d6447d47f55944d1512bbfca","tid":948813,"uid":155095,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"quote":{"pid":"700b038a7cdd3dcff229e3dbf101913e8fb944b8","tid":948813,"uid":94828,"like":40,"dislike":2,"score":38,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:51:16.000Z","msg":"幾時有新種狗<br />\n改佢叫習近平"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-12-20T10:54:05.000Z","msg":"習氏狼條脊甲<br />\n<br />\n習氏狼條脊甲（學名：Rhyzodiastes xii），一種昆蟲，屬於條脊甲亞科（英語：Rhysodinae），在中國海南島發現。這種小型甲蟲數量稀少，有念珠狀的觸角，居住在樹皮及腐木中，食用腐化後的樹皮。<br />\n<br 